          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Response Time</h3>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <p>• <strong>Research inquiries:</strong> 2-3 business days</p>
              <p>• <strong>Consulting projects:</strong> 1-2 business days</p>
              <p>• <strong>Speaking engagements:</strong> 3-5 business days</p>
              <p>• <strong>General questions:</strong> 1 week</p>
